itifs de formation en alternance ont pris de l’ampleur aujourd’hui, tout en épousant des approches variées.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aEducation, Cooperative. 0aPhysical education teachersxTraining of. 7aEDUCATION / General.2bisacsh1 aAdrián, Cordoba, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAnne-Sophie, Aubin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBenoît, Lenzen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBernard, Poussin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBorges, Cecilia, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCecilia, Borges, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDelphine, Tremblay-Gagnon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDenis, Loizon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDijnane, Vedovatto, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrançois, Vandercleyen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGhislain, Carlier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJean-François, Desbiens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLarissa C., Benites, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLenzen, Benoit, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLoizon, Denis, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMatthieu, Laugier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMaurice, Tardif, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNathalie, Gal-Petitfaux, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNicolas, Gaudillere, econtributor.4ctb4https://